\[
\frac{2}{5}\;\div\;\frac{3}{10}
\;=\;
\frac{2}{5}\;\times\;\frac{10}{3}
\]

**Step 2 – Multiply the numerators and the denominators**

\[
\frac{2}{5}\times\frac{10}{3}
=\frac{2\cdot 10}{5\cdot 3}
=\frac{20}{15}
\]

